data.title: Digital Supply Chain Management
data.meta_description: Data lies at the beginning of any efforts to optimise business performance and processes. That is also where our expertise begins. Automate your logistics for the future.
data.text:
Cookie Name:Â __hstc

Storage duration:Â 6 months

Description:Â The main cookie for visitor tracking. It contains the domain, the user token (hubspotutk), the first timestamp (of the first visit), the last timestamp (of the last visit), the current timestamp (for this visit) and the session number (increases with each subsequent session).

Cookie Name:Â hubspotutk

Storage duration:Â 6 months

Description:Â This cookie tracks the identity of a visitor. This cookie is transferred to the HubSpot software when a form is submitted and is used when contacts are duplicated. It contains an opaque GUID to represent the current visitor.

Cookie Name:Â __hssc

Storage duration:Â 30 minutes

Description: This cookie tracks sessions. It is used to determine whether the HubSpot software needs to increment the session count and timestamps in the __hstc cookie. It contains the domain, the number of page views (viewCount, increases with each page view [pageView] in a session) and the session start timestamp.

Cookie Name:Â __hssrc

Storage duration: End of session

Description:Â Whenever the HubSpot software changes the session cookie, this cookie is also set. This is used to determine whether the visitor has restarted the browser. If this cookie is not present when HubSpot manages cookies, it is considered a new session. It contains the value "1", if present.

Cookie Name: li_oatml

Storage duration: 30 days

Description: This cookie is used to identify LinkedIn members outside of LinkedIn for promotional and analytical purposes outside of the designated countries and, for a limited time, for promotional purposes in the designated countries.

Cookie Name: lidc

Storage duration: 24 hours

Description: This cookie optimises the selection of the data centre.

Cookie Name:Â lissc

Storage duration:Â 365 days

Description:Â This cookie ensures that all cookies in this browser use the same SameSite attribute.

Cookie Name:Â s_sq

Storage duration:Â Session

Description:Â Adobe Analytics uses this cookie to store information about the previous link that a user clicked on.

Cookie Name:Â AMCVS_14215E3D5995C57C0A495C55%40AdobeOrgÂ Â Storage duration:Â Session

Description:Â For the Adobe Experience Cloud, this cookie indicates when a session began.

Cookie Name:Â lang

Storage duration:Â Session

Description:Â This cookie remembers the language setting of a user.

Cookie Name:Â s_cc

Storage duration:Â Session

Description:Â This cookie is used by Adobe Analytics to determine whether cookies are enabled.

Cookie Name:Â UserMatchHistory

Storage duration:Â 30 days

Description:Â This cookie is used to synchronize the IDs of LinkedIn Ads.

Cookie Name:Â Â AMCV_14215E3D5995C57C0A495C55%40AdobeOrgÂ Â

Storage duration:Â 180 days

Description:Â This is a unique identifier for the Adobe Experience Cloud.

Cookie Name:Â bcookie

Storage duration:Â 730 days

Description:Â This cookie is a browser identification. It is used to uniquely identify devices accessing LinkedIn in order to detect misuse of the platform.
